<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=The_Boston_Globe&action=edit&section=12.php.html" title="Edit section: Prices">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Prices">Prices</span></h2>
<p><i>The Boston Globe</i> prices are: $1.25 daily, $3.50 Sunday/Thanksgiving Day.</p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=The_Boston_Globe&action=edit&section=13.php.html" title="Edit section: Paywall">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Paywall">Paywall</span></h3>
<p>The Boston Globe charges a fee for visits to its website by visitors who are not subscribers.<sup id="cite_ref-45" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-45"><span>[</span>45<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
